{"tid":1677802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日重點係黑警打壓和平集會，唔係我地唔爭氣","createTime":"2019-10-27T10:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T11:07:29.000Z","uid":58719,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"145bfc45bad438ddaa62fb991934f6ccf52862b6","tid":1677802,"uid":58719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"係，一日未成功，一日都係失敗緊<br />\n但係要繼續行動先有可能贏<br />\n與其喺度話自己人失敗無用豬隊友無膽<br />\n不如諗吓今日個結果仲有咩嘢價值反映俾其他人睇<br />\n藍絲都不割同幫班犬兜啦<br />\n<br />\n今日個活動係和平集會、<span style=\"font-size: large;\">和平集會</span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和平集會</span>、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和平集會</span></span>呀！<br />\n依家係連集會都未正式開始已經搵陶輝出嚟捉人，又用胡椒水噴傷殘人士同射大陸毒製催淚彈毒殺市民呀！<br />\n又唔肯批不反對通知書，又出蒙面法<br />\n香港人嘅集會同言論自由繼續被港共政府打壓<br />\n今晚又戒嚴宵禁封鎖公共交通工具喇<br />\n係咪又係時候經Tweet 俾外國知香港唔適投資喇！<br />\n<br />\n係，上面啲point大家都聽過，但都係唔可以慣㗎！！<br />\n幫幫手唔好再圍內互插住喇好嗎？"},{"pid":"03ca692a92a8eeac314f8dfe182eb960f3c900b0","tid":1677802,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e3ee0d08eb37669f19f54c7952568cc0b2571b","tid":1677802,"uid":58719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:09:21.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"240d57d786144ff8b99bb2b4b9948c563adddb82","tid":1677802,"uid":58719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"a1cd8ded6e31183b2940e5ea7707bf547eaa40ff","tid":1677802,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"Better than 互屌"},{"pid":"4aa5d2c760cde37f06d353022b8481cf677e0625","tid":1677802,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:16:31.000Z","msg":"試下申請18區<br />\n<br />\n看下佢會唔會18區都拒絕"},